  <topic>Row count</topic>
  <description>
    When the Orientation property is set to 'Columns' and the Row flow property is set to 'TBLR' (top-to-bottom left-to-right), then the Row count property
    will appear. This property simply sets how many Rows should be used to display the Check Box choices.
  </description>
